</span>)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a parametrized adjunction `F ⊣₂ G` between bifunctors, and structures\n`sq₁₂ : F.PushoutObjObj f₁ f₂` and `sq₁₃ : G.PullbackObjObj f₁ f₃`, there are\nas many commutative squares with left map `sq₁₂.ι` and right map `f₃`\nas commutative squares with left map `f₂` and right map `sq₁₃.π`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/LiftingProperties/ParametrizedAdjunction.html#CategoryTheory.ParametrizedAdjunction.arrowHomEquiv","kind":"def","line":43,"name":"CategoryTheory.ParametrizedAdjunction.arrowHomEquiv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/LiftingProperties/ParametrizedAdjunction.lean#L43-L90"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.LiftingProperties.Basic","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Adjunction.Parametrized","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Limits.Shapes.Pullback.PullbackObjObj"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.CategoryTheory.LiftingProperties.ParametrizedAdjunction"}